      "width": 1056.0,
      "height": 12.5,
      "text": "\u26d4 POST-PILOT M3 SPOKE \u2014 NOT in the pilot \u00b7 central node = LabSolution's OWN on-prem datacenter in PH (M2 public cloud NOT used) \u00b7 built later as a change-control delta on the validated M1 base",
