    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t00075f39b83",
      "x": 99.49999999999994,
      "y": 615.0,
      "width": 781.0000000000001,
      "height": 50.0,
      "text": "\u26a0 COMPLIANCE EXTRA-WORK GATE before this spoke (docs/compliance/m3-sync-compliance-gate.md) \u2014 LabSolution becomes a PIP with physical custody:\nown DPS registration (NPC) \u00b7 head DPA + middleware flow-down \u00b7 own breach apparatus \u00b7 central key custody\ndatacenter physical-security / BCP \u00b7 re-run threat model + PIA \u00b7 supplier-qualify hosting (ISO 15189 Cl. 6.8)\n\u2192 then validate the spoke as a change-control delta on the validated M1 base (REQ-QMS-03).",
      "originalText": "\u26a0 COMPLIANCE EXTRA-WORK GATE before this spoke (docs/compliance/m3-sync-compliance-gate.md) \u2014 LabSolution becomes a PIP with physical custody:\nown DPS registration (NPC) \u00b7 head DPA + middleware flow-down \u00b7 own breach apparatus \u00b7 central key custody\ndatacenter physical-security / BCP \u00b7 re-run threat model + PIA \u00b7 supplier-qualify hosting (ISO 15189 Cl. 6.8)\n\u2192 then validate the spoke as a change-control delta on the validated M1 base (REQ-QMS-03).",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "gate",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
